org.bukkit.configuration.ConfigurationOptions

  • ConfigurationOptionsを使用しているパッケージ 
    パッケージ 説明
    org.bukkit.configuration
    Classes dedicated to handling a plugin's runtime configuration.
    org.bukkit.configuration.file
    Classes dedicated facilitating configurations to be read and stored on the filesystem.

    • org.bukkit.configurationでのConfigurationOptionsの使用

      org.bukkit.configurationでのConfigurationOptionsのサブクラス 
      修飾子とタイプ クラスと説明
      class  MemoryConfigurationOptions
      Various settings for controlling the input and output of a MemoryConfiguration
      ConfigurationOptionsを返すorg.bukkit.configurationのメソッド 
      修飾子とタイプ メソッドと説明
      ConfigurationOptions ConfigurationOptions.copyDefaults(boolean value)
      Sets if the Configuration should copy values from its default Configuration directly.
      ConfigurationOptions Configuration.options()
      Gets the ConfigurationOptions for this Configuration.
      ConfigurationOptions ConfigurationOptions.pathSeparator(char value)
      Sets the char that will be used to separate ConfigurationSections This value does not affect how the Configuration is stored, only in how you access the data.
